metadata.name: Chidz Default Balloondles
metadata.description:
If you own a "Chidz Default Balloondles" token you'll be entitled to your own balloondle or balloondoop nft. You must own the a dooplicator or the doodle of which the balloondle and balloondoop wll be made of. If you own multiple doodles for example 3. If you want a balloondle for each, then you'll need to own 3 "Chidz Default Balloondles" tokens. If you don't own either, no worries you can still collect for the art :).

The hi-res file has been included as an 'unlockable content' so you can download and print the artwork and frame in your home/office. :)
